### Register a new user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "johndoe",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "roleId": 1,
  "phoneNumber": "123-456-7890",
  "address": {
    "zip": "12345",
    "country": "USA",
    "street": "123 Main St",
    "province": "NY"
  }
}

###

### Login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Validate Token (replace YOUR_TOKEN_HERE with actual token from login response)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/auth/validate
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Get all products (protected endpoint - requires authentication)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Get current user info (using token)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/auth/validate
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
